{
  "analysis": "We have cached FPbase full data, PDB FASTA/metadata, and DHFR. The previous gather script crashed due to `len(None)`. We still need robust analysis to select donor/acceptor with spectra matching the 505/610 filter cube, verify the molecule binder for the target SMILES, retrieve the antibody-target (HER2) sequence, then assemble/codon-optimize and validate the gBlock.",
  "plan": "Run a corrected `analyze_components.py` that:
1. Loads FPbase and prints exact/near donor (ex ~505) and acceptor (em ~610) candidates, prioritizing FPbase entries with PDB IDs from pdb_ids.txt.
2. Fetches PDBe ligand/binding-site data for all PDB IDs and saves/prints SMILES/keyword matches.
3. Fetches/prints HER2 UniProt P04626 sequence.
